OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FParty leader Zack Polanski said the
OL,8,FGreens would back a 10mph speed limit
OL,9,Fin London "where appropriate" and even
OL,10,Fraised the prospect of challenging Sir
OL,11,FKeir Starmer at the next General
OL,12,FElection.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News London at the
OL,15,Fparty's local election launch in
OL,16,FLewisham, Mr Polanski said he wanted
OL,17,Fto encourage Londoners to travel by
OL,18,Fbike or Tube.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
