OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FAsked whether he wanted a 10mph limit
OL,8,Ffor people who had to use a car, Mr
OL,9,FPolanski said: "I want to see a
OL,10,Freduction in harm and danger on our
OL,11,Froads.
OL,13,F"What that looks like will often be up
OL,14,Fto the local area, so there will be
OL,15,Fplaces where it is appropriate.
OL,17,F"There are areas in Hackney where
OL,18,Fpeople should be able to ride their
OL,19,Fbike everywhere. In fact, they can
OL,20,Falready.
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,F"They can get on the Tube, they've got
OL,8,Fa bus, and unless you're disabled,
OL,9,Fthere's often not really a good reason
OL,10,Fto be in a car.
OL,12,F"There are other places, though, in
OL,13,Fthe outer boroughs, for instance,
OL,14,Fwhere you might be lucky if you get a
OL,15,Fbus every few hours, if not sometimes
OL,16,Fevery couple of days. There, it
OL,17,Fclearly wouldn't be appropriate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,F"So I don't think it's a blanket
OL,8,Fmeasure for London. I think it's about
OL,9,Frecognising that it's up to local
OL,10,Fcouncillors in each area to understand
OL,11,Fthe needs of their communities."
OL,13,FLondoners will go to the polls on
OL,14,FThursday 7 May in each of London's 32
OL,15,Fboroughs, in what will be a real test
OL,16,Fof Labour's support. The party
OL,17,Fcurrently controls 21 boroughs.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
