PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FThe Green Party leader said his party
OL,8,Fwas most hopeful of performing well in
OL,9,FHackney and Lewisham, while Islington
OL,10,Fand Camden were "places to watch".
OL,12,F"I think Hackney is clearly the first
OL,13,Fplace to look," Mr Polanski added.
OL,15,F"We've got an incredible candidate in
OL,16,FZoe Garbutt, my colleague on the
OL,17,FLondon Assembly.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@aO]tD@AOUuD@OO]wD@AOUxD@Cxr
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,F"So I see every day the difference
OL,8,Fshe'll make to Londoners. But frankly,
OL,9,Ffor people who live in Hackney, I
OL,10,Fthink that will be a game changer`not
OL,11,Fjust for Hackney, but for London and
OL,12,Fthe entire country.
OL,14,F"We've got Liam Shrivastava running
OL,15,Ffor mayor of Lewisham, and I think
OL,16,Fincreasingly it looks like we could do
OL,17,Freally well there.
OL,19,F"I'm not complacent, though`I'm just
OL,20,Fconfident about how we're going to
OL,21,Fperform.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,F"Places like Islington and Camden
OL,8,Fclearly are places to watch as well."
OL,10,FAsked about his own political
OL,11,Fambitions, Zack Polanski said he could
OL,12,Fstand against Sir Keir Starmer in his
OL,13,FHolborn and St Pancras constituency at
OL,14,Fthe next General Election.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
