OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FHe said: "I think there's a whole
OL,8,Fseries of seats, particularly around
OL,9,Fwhere I live - whether that's Hackney
OL,10,FNorth and Stoke Newington, where I'm
OL,11,Fbased now, Hackney South, Walthamstow,
OL,12,FTottenham, and indeed Holborn and St
OL,13,FPancras.
OL,15,F"I lived in Camden for over 10 years,
OL,16,Fbut I've not decided exactly where I'm
OL,17,Fgoing to run yet. I'll announce that
OL,18,Fmuch nearer to the general election."
OL,26,@oD@JOUwD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
