PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1775931065
OL,3,CGreen leader backs 10mph and could
OL,4,Cchallenge Keir Starmer at General
OL,5,CElection
OL,7,FAsked again if the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fcould face Mr Polanski as a challenger
OL,9,Fat the next election, he replied:
OL,10,F"It's possible.
OL,12,F"Whether you're the Prime Minister,
OL,13,FDavid Lammy, or Stella Creasy, whether
OL,14,Fit's me or another Green candidate, we
OL,15,Fare coming for your seat."
